            ><br />works on things that are not suppose to work
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden">
            <CldImage
              src="alex-min_ypkkz2"
              alt="Alex"
