          <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Daniyar</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto">
            <span class="font-mono text-purple-500"
              >tg: <a
