            hardware is.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <span class="text-4xl font-mono text-gray-400">A</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Arthur</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto">
            <span class="font-mono text-purple-500"
              >tg: <a
                href="https://t.me/ktnlvr"
                data-umami-event="telegram-artur"
                target="_blank"
                class="hover:underline">@ktnlvr</a
              ></span
            ><br />knows just enough math to be dangerous.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 mx-auto mb-2 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <span class="text-4xl font-mono text-gray-400">V</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-mono mb-0.5 text-gray-900">Vlad</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-xs text-gray-600 leading-tight w-32 mx-auto">
            <span class="font-mono text-purple-500"
              >tg: <a
                href="https://t.me/VladyslavBM"
                data-umami-event="telegram-vlad"
                target="_blank"
                class="hover:underline">@VladyslavBM</a
              ></span
            ><br />solving things nobody wants to deal with.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Partners Section -->
      <div class="mb-6 font-sans text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
        <h3 id="partners" class="font-mono text-gray-900 mb-3 md:mb-4">Backed by people who get it:</h3>
        <p>
          Industry partners and universities support the lab with equipment, knowledge, and connections to real-world challenges. This lets builders access industry-grade hardware and stay connected to the broader technology ecosystem. Check out our <a
            href="/hardware"
            class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors"
            >hardware page</a
          > to see what's available.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-16 fade-in max-w-5xl mx-auto">

        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 sm:gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-8"
        >
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://varjo.com/" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-varjo">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/varjo.png"
                  alt="Varjo"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://doublepoint.com/" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-doublepoint">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/doublepoint.png"
                  alt="Doublepoint"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://alifsemi.com/" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-alif">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/Alif_Semiconductor_logo.webp"
                  alt="Alif Semiconductor"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://www.seetruetechnologies.com/" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-seetrue">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/seetrue-technologies.png"
                  alt="SeeTrue Technologies"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://www.aalto.fi/" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-aalto">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/aalto-logo.png"
                  alt="Aalto University"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://www.kyutech.ac.jp/" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-kyutech">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/kyutech-logo.png"
                  alt="Kyushu Institute of Technology"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://ignite.aaltoes.com" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-ignite">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/ignite-logo.png"
                  alt="Ignite"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 md:p-4 lg:p-6 text-center">
            <a href="https://wihurinrahasto.fi" target="_blank" data-umami-event="partner-wihuri">
              <div
                class="w-24 h-16 sm:w-32 sm:h-20 md:w-40 md:h-24 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <img
                  src="/images/companies-logo/wihuri-logo.png"
                  alt="Wihuri"
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                />
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Space Section -->
      <div class="mb-8 font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
        <p>
          We're located at <a
            href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Startup+Sauna,+Puumiehenkuja+5,+02150+Espoo,+Finland"
            class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors"
            data-umami-event="location-sus"
            >Startup Sauna</a
          > at Aalto University, second floor. Come to Aaltoes co-working space and ask for Thinkin' Rocks, or ping us on <a
            href="https://t.me/+rxHNt6GA4-o1NWUy"
            class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors"
            target="_blank"
            >Telegram</a
          >. The space is open when someone's there to let you in. For regular access, join the community and start building.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Space Photos Carousel -->
      <SpaceCarousel
        images={[
          {
            src: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dby6mmmff/image/upload/w_800,h_600,c_fill/whole-area_v4qg1y",
            alt: "Main Workspace",
            caption: "Collaborative work area with desks, monitors, and tools."
          },
          {
            src: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dby6mmmff/image/upload/w_800,h_600,c_fill/shelf-area_sfnum4",
            alt: "Hardware & Storage Area",
            caption: "Storage area with shelves for hardware and materials."
          },
          {
            src: "https://res.cloudinary.com/dby6mmmff/image/upload/w_800,h_600,c_fill/chill-area_iz650y",
            alt: "Chill Area",
            caption: "Multi-purpose area for demos, talks, and hanging out."
          }
        ]}
        client:load
      />
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2
        id="faq"
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6"
      >
        FAQ
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-mono mb-2 text-gray-900">
            How do I join?
          </h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-gray-700">
            Join our Telegram chat, introduce yourself, and come by the lab. Start working on something. Access deepens as you build.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-mono mb-2 text-gray-900">
            What can I build here?
          </h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-gray-700">
            AI experiments, robotics systems, hardware prototypes, research projects, creative technology. Priority goes to active, collaborative projects that share knowledge with the community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-mono mb-2 text-gray-900">
            Does it cost anything?
          </h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-gray-700">
            Basic participation is free. For intensive equipment use or long-term projects, we may ask for contributions to cover maintenance. We keep barriers low while maintaining sustainability.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-mono mb-2 text-gray-900">
            Can I find collaborators?
          </h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-gray-700">
            Yes. Many arrive without a team and find one here. Skills overlap, ideas collide, unexpected things emerge. The Telegram chat and build sessions are where collaboration starts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-mono mb-2 text-gray-900">
            When are workshops held?
          </h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-gray-700">
            Regularly. Structured trainings on specific tools, open build nights where everyone works on their own projects. Both matter. Check Telegram for schedules.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-mono mb-2 text-gray-900">
            How do I stay updated?
          </h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-gray-700">
            Join the Telegram chat. Events, workshops, and spontaneous build sessions are announced there. It's also where questions get answered and ideas find collaborators.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
